Open Letter from Big Mack Trump

some people say i write the best words — it’s true

Folks,


Hi, it’s me your President, Donald J. Trump.


I’d like to say to all the great American Patriots that there’s nothing more American and based than our American truck drivers. It’s true, they are very American and very based. If there ever was something as based and American it would be the MacDonald’s Big Mac. Both are truly very American and very based - so based I decided to become a Big Mack Truck myself. Some say, I am the biggest Mack truck they've ever seen. It’s true, I am.


That’s why I’d like to announce that from today forward, you can now call me Big Mack Trump, that’s what everyone is calling me. They call me that because I love Big Macs, and I love big Macks.


In the true hearts of American Patriots we know one thing binds us all. That is the hot delicious taste of two all-beef patties, special sauce, lettuce, cheese, pickles, onions on a beautiful sesame seed bun.


It’s my favorite, and I know it’s going to be yours.


Love,

Your President,

Donald “Big Mack” Trump
